{"tid":704040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"基金公司CEO只穿內褲被燒死　疑手機充電爆炸","createTime":"2018-06-16T06:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T02:24:59.000Z","uid":13468,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9d3b7e7563d5aacffb2334c8028c619a11e7f138","tid":704040,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:39:21.000Z","msg":"基金公司CEO只穿內褲被燒死　疑手機充電爆炸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞一名基金公司總執行長納茲林，在14日中午被發現於家中被燒死，死時僅穿一條內褲。家屬懷疑，可能是納茲林的手機在充電時爆炸起火，燒死正在睡午覺的納茲林。<br />\n<br />\n據馬來西亞《中國報》報導，納茲林是搖籃私人基金公司(Cradle Fund Sdn Bhd)的CEO，不過在14日中午左右，納茲林的家中突然起火，火勢撲滅後，警消也在屋內發現納茲林的遺體。報導指出，納茲林被發現時身上僅穿內褲，被燒死在屋內，而納茲林的妻子和4名孩子則及時逃生。<br />\n<br />\n家屬指出，案發當時納茲林正在睡午覺，懷疑是手機充電爆炸釀悲劇，也導致納茲林後腦勺嚴重灼傷，隨後更燒到納茲林的床鋪。家屬也指出，納茲林是3C愛好者，擁有黑莓和華為兩個品牌的智慧型手機，目前家屬不排除是手機充電釀禍，但並不確定是哪支手機充電出問題。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n發稿：07:01<br />\n更新：12:42<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180616/1374348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180616%2F1374348&d=Xss1rbCGGQoh133a3dErLMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=ee211ad2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180616%2F1374348&h=de599325\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180616/1374348</a>"},{"pid":"b589f24f251c9fadd68ee3b8553d77d002e8629a","tid":704040,"uid":13468,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:40:04.000Z","msg":"華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb5fa9a52814db72f0d9c69f460eff2271b9e2e","tid":704040,"uid":33263,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b589f24f251c9fadd68ee3b8553d77d002e8629a","tid":704040,"uid":13468,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:40:04.000Z","msg":"華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmo