give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4e4f29d25f5f76d091cbb68d04691e137faed6","tid":704040,"uid":72280,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:29:56.000Z","msg":"似大馬政治暗殺<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n據《星島日報》報導，45歲死者納茲林（Nazsrin Hassan）是搖籃基金公司（Cradle Fund Sdn Bhd）行政總裁，該基金公司隸屬馬來西亞財政部，成立於2003年。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然家屬懷疑是手機爆炸造成納茲林死亡，但許多馬來西亞網友認為「案情不單純」，揣測與馬國政府貪污舞弊有關，有人說「沒那麼簡單！虧公款？」、「這個基金是財政部的&hellip;所以事情應該不是那麼簡單」、「看來沒那麼簡單，恐與巫統一系列的舞弊案有關」。<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n柔佛洲早排死左個反對派領袖<br />\n政府又是屈佢係油站用手機所以先爆炸<br />\n但住係果度的人都知係汽車炸彈⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n利申：有親戚住新山"},{"pid":"476fb868eb75586119785eb264581ac0f95ba63d","tid":704040,"uid":15984,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b15dffe117fe7b444ae190c62eef1784e2e7f21a","tid":704040,"uid":37111,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:05:49.000Z","msg":"黑莓balckberry係TCL設計+代工 咪又係中國野<br />\n華為就更加唔使講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:31:43.000Z","msg":"究竟幾ON9 嘅人先會用中國製造嘅電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同自殺無分別"},{"pid":"de028be138c106dbcb62ad54e7e97bc447ef280c","tid":704040,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:34:43.000Z","msg":"納吉布早幾年被人告過用對外基建同石油項目貪污<br />\n最後因為頂證佢的人突然消失先告唔成"},{"pid":"bffcbd36625a12e861b51455b911ab7e6b725865","tid":704040,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T08:42:25.000Z","msg":"遙控炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你支又贏"},{"pid":"ce0a3f7e582718096b32794d4320768f1bbfe1da","tid":704040,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike"